‚ÄúThere‚Äôs no sense in waiting around man,‚Äù I said.  ‚ÄúI‚Äôll tell you what, why don‚Äôt we all go.  Just the three of us. I‚Äôll pay.  It‚Äôll be a group date.  I‚Äôll even let you guys hold hands.‚Äù

