This piece isn't meant to be comforting. It forces readers to face the darkest possibilities alongside those glimmers of true transcendence. Leaving in both the beauty AND the ugliness without tidy resolutions‚Ä¶ that's not only honest, but has true power to challenge the way minds, human or otherwise, interact with the world.

